OL,3,CChurch in Wales votes to continue
OL,4,Coffering same-sex blessings
OL,6,FThe Church in Wales has voted to
OL,7,Fcontinue providing blessings for
OL,8,Fcouples in same-sex civil partnerships
OL,9,For civil marriages.
OL,11,FFive years ago, the Church began a
OL,12,Ftrial period after deciding it was
OL,13,F"pastorally unsustainable" to not
OL,14,Foffer a formal blessing provision.
OL,15,FAlthough clergy can decide to opt out
OL,16,Fof conducting the blessings.
OL,18,FThat five-year period was due to come
OL,19,Fto an end in September this year.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
