OL,3,CChurch in Wales votes to continue
OL,4,Coffering same-sex blessings
OL,6,FIn Llandudno on Wednesday (15 April),
OL,7,Fthe Church's governing body debated a
OL,8,Fmotion to make the blessings a
OL,9,Fpermanent offering.
OL,11,FIn order to pass, it needed a two
OL,12,Fthirds majority in each of the
OL,13,Fgoverning body's three orders -
OL,14,FBishops, Clergy and Laity. All five
OL,15,FBishops voted in favour, the clergy
OL,16,Fvoted 32 - 7 in favour, and the laity
OL,17,F48 - 8 in favour.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
