OL,3,CChurch in Wales votes to continue
OL,4,Coffering same-sex blessings
OL,6,FThe Church in Wales does not marry
OL,7,Fsame-sex couples - however it has said
OL,8,Fthat proposals will be brought forward
OL,9,Fin April 2027 to allow changes to
OL,10,Fhappen so same-sex marriages could
OL,11,Ftake place within the Church.
OL,13,FThis comes after listening exercises
OL,14,Fin 2025 where the Church found a
OL,15,Fmajority "in favour of the view that
OL,16,Fthe time is right to offer equal
OL,17,Fmarriage".
