OL,3,CChurch in Wales votes to continue
OL,4,Coffering same-sex blessings
OL,6,FSpeaking about Wednesday's vote, the
OL,7,FMost Revd Cherry Vann, Archbishop of
OL,8,FWales, said: "I want to thank everyone
OL,9,Ffor the ways in which this debate was
OL,10,Fconducted ` calmly, and with mutual
OL,11,Frespect.
