PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F469A1776679572
OL,3,CChurch in Wales votes to continue
OL,4,Coffering same-sex blessings
OL,6,F"The Bench of Bishops and I recognise
OL,7,Fthat this is an issue about which
OL,8,Fpeople hold strong convictions. We
OL,9,Fwant everybody to be able to hold
OL,10,Ftheir views with integrity whilst not
OL,11,Flosing sight of the image of God that
OL,12,Fresides in all of us. We want to build
OL,13,Fa church that can make space for each
OL,14,Fother whatever our different
OL,15,Fperspectives."
